HEADWORD: halfback
<hw>halfback</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Football)</fld> <def>A person who
plays the position of halfback{2} on a football team.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> running back.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The position of either of two players on a football
team who typically begins each play behind the line and on either side
of the quarterback.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

